{"title_page": "Nature's Variety", "text_new": "{{thirdparty|date=November 2017}}\n{{orphan|date=November 2017}}\n{{notability|date=November 2017}}\n{{COI|date=November 2017}}\n{{Infobox company\n|name  = Nature's Variety\n|logo  = Nature's Variety Company Logo.jpg\n|location      = [[St. Louis, Missouri]] [[Lincoln, Nebraska]]\n|industry      = [[Pet food]]\n|products      = Dog food, cat food, grain-free pet food, raw pet food\n|homepage      = {{URL|naturesvariety.com}}\n}}\n\n'''Nature's Variety''' is a pet food company, wholly owned by [[Barcelona|Barcelona, Spain]]\u2013based [[Agrolimen]]. With manufacturing facilities in [[Lincoln, Nebraska]], and headquarters in [[St. Louis, Missouri]], Nature's Variety specializes in natural, raw, and grain-free foods for dogs and cats, including dry [[Dog food|kibble]] and canned varieties.\n\n==Brands==\nNature's Variety owns and manages the Instinct and Prairie brands.\n\nInstinct is a full line of grain-free and gluten-free foods for dogs and cats available in a variety of forms and flavors.<ref>[http://www.instinctpetfood.com/product-choices Instinct Product Assortment]</ref>\n\nPrairie is a line of canned and kibble dog and cat food that utilizes meat as the first ingredient, whole grains and fruits and vegetables.\n\n==Food safety==\nNature's Variety uses a food safety protocol called [[Pascalization|high pressure processing]] (HPP or pascalization) in its raw food. HPP is a process that kills pathogenic bacteria through high-pressure, water-based technology.\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n*https://www.naturesvariety.com/our-brands\n*https://www.petfoodindustry.com/directories/211-top-pet-food-companies-current-data/listing/12291-agrolimen-sa\n\n==External Links==\n{{Official|naturesvariety.com}}\n\n[[Category:Food and drink companies of the United States]]\n[[Category:Dog food brands]]\n[[Category:Cat food brands]]\n", "text_old": "{{thirdparty|date=November 2017}}\n{{orphan|date=November 2017}}\n{{notability|date=November 2017}}\n{{COI|date=November 2017}}\n{{Infobox company\n|name  = Nature's Variety\n|logo  = Nature's Variety Company Logo.jpg\n|location      = [[St. Louis, Missouri]] [[Lincoln, Nebraska]]\n|industry      = [[Pet food]]\n|products      = Dog food, cat food, grain-free pet food, raw pet food\n|homepage = [http://naturesvariety.com Nature's Variety Site]\n}}\n\n'''Nature's Variety''' is a pet food company, wholly owned by [[Barcelona|Barcelona, Spain]]\u2013based [[Agrolimen]]. With manufacturing facilities in [[Lincoln, Nebraska]], and headquarters in [[St. Louis, Missouri]], Nature's Variety specializes in natural, raw, and grain-free foods for dogs and cats, including dry [[Dog food|kibble]] and canned varieties.\n\n==Brands==\nNature's Variety owns and manages the Instinct and Prairie brands.\n\nInstinct is a full line of grain-free and gluten-free foods for dogs and cats available in a variety of forms and flavors.<ref>[http://www.instinctpetfood.com/product-choices Instinct Product Assortment]</ref>\n\nPrairie is a line of canned and kibble dog and cat food that utilizes meat as the first ingredient, whole grains and fruits and vegetables.\n\n==Food safety==\nNature's Variety uses a food safety protocol called [[Pascalization|high pressure processing]] (HPP or pascalization) in its raw food. HPP is a process that kills pathogenic bacteria through high-pressure, water-based technology.\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n*https://www.naturesvariety.com/our-brands\n*https://www.petfoodindustry.com/directories/211-top-pet-food-companies-current-data/listing/12291-agrolimen-sa\n\n==External Links==\n{{Official|naturesvariety.com}}\n\n[[Category:Food and drink companies of the United States]]\n[[Category:Dog food brands]]\n[[Category:Cat food brands]]\n", "name_user": "GentlemanGhost", "label": "safe", "comment": "Standardizing infobox", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nature%27s_Variety"}
